# Results are generated, not committed. Committed exceptions: the report,
# figures, and the tiny per-seed metrics_*.json that back the n=11 headline
# (so the result reproduces on a fresh clone; raw logs/checkpoints stay out).
results/*/**
!results/*/**/
!results/**/metrics_*.json
!results/REPORT.md
!results/*.png

# Large data files
data/failures/*.parquet

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
